frames.caption: In a surreal farm setting, a gigantic cow towers over the landscape, surrounded by farmers. Some farmers are on ladders tending to the cow, while others stand on the ground observing the scene.
frames.description: The scene depicts a whimsical farm where a colossal cow stands in the center, dwarfing the surrounding farmers and animals. The setting is rural, with rolling hills and a barn in the background, creating a peaceful yet fantastical atmosphere.

frames.caption: In a surreal pastoral scene, a gigantic cow towers over a farmyard, with several farmers interacting with it. Some farmers are on ladders attending to the cow, while others stand on the ground observing or tending to smaller cows.
frames.description: The image depicts a whimsical farm setting where a colossal cow is the central focus. Farmers are actively engaging with the cow, using ladders to reach its back, while smaller cows and farm structures are visible in the background.
